				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">..why did they nerf Pet Canni? 
<br />

<br />
necros can do HP to Mana then Lifetap to regain HPs which gives them almost zero down time, yes?
<br />

<br />
Pet Canni still gave us downtime, not alot but it wasn't like we could tell the mob we're currently soloing "Time out! i'm OOM!...give me a sec..<1 minute later> ok go!" i'm sure with SM you could have summoned a 2nd pet and cannied him til FOM but it's still some downtime, not like pet canni was giving us a continuous stream of mobs with zero downtime.
<br />

<br />
also our pet heals aren't the best, but instead of trying to add a new heal and balance it so "we're not too powerful and need to be nerfed again" wouldn't it be better if sony just gave mages Healing gift and Healing Adept AA?
<br />

<br />
Druids have it and they can charm/dc some nice animal pets.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1001505" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Master Kavar </a>
