			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Speaking of the necro "hp to mana/lifetap" thing...
<br />

<br />
Did you know that if there's no mobs around, and a necro has a mage nearby with a clay bracelet (the instant eye of zomm bracelet from Temple of Sol Ro), or any other class that can summon an eye of zomm for that matter, there's a little trick they can do.  Do HP to mana, then have the mage (or whoever) make an eye of zomm, then cast lifetap on it.  The eye dies instantly, but the necro gets the full lifetap recourse.  Now, what that essentially means is that as long as a necro has an eye-summoner around, they have absolutely no downtime. I guess that's what makes mage-necro duo kiting so effective.
<br />

<br />
And yes, I agree we should get Healing Adept/Gift AA's.  It's not like we're gonna be healing anyone else.<br />_________________<br />--<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=559376" target="_blank" class="postlink">Arc</a>--
<br />
62nd level Arch Mage
<br />
Tunare Server</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
