<br />

<br />
It was extremely nice that you could generate huge quantities of mana. I basically didn't bother with KEI, because I did well on my own. Using monster summon II worked well and if you could use Rathes Son the regen was phenomenal.
<br />

<br />
Secondly....
<br />

<br />
Because this was in the game and was a well known trick and was used by many it was a serious stopper in any development of the mage class. If anything was introduced to the game that could increase the the hp of a pet, then cannipetting just became even better.
<br />

<br />
All the pet development AA's and elemental draw/syphon is a direct result of cannipetting being removed and the new proposed zoning pets are also a result hereof.
<br />

<br />
GET OVER IT!! The game is better and more interesting with it removed!
