				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Not that I know of, but you can summon an elementalkin (the level 4 pet) and kill it with elemental draw/siphon, and still get the full recourse.
<br />

<br />
I don't think that pet spells work on eyes, I don't think they're considered "pets" in the traditional sense.  I do know, however, that any type of lifetap spell works on an eye, even though it only has like 1 hit point, and you get the full recourse effect.  Necro's especially like this little fact. =)<br />_________________<br />--<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=559376" target="_blank" class="postlink">Arc</a>--
<br />
62nd level Arch Mage
<br />
